## Database Setup
1. Download the database backup from https://drive.google.com/file/d/1CBWa23B8afSynl0WXOqQJ5gthzbr6X_X/view?usp=sharing
2. Open SQL Server Management Studio (SSMS).
3. Restore the `.bak` file using "Restore Database" option.
4. Change the connection string in App.config to your connection string.
